@ENDNODE CDNormalSpeed

@NODE CDSpeed "RI CompactDisk Lib V2.5"

@{fg shine}Statement: CDSpeed@{fg text}
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Modes : Amiga/Blitz
Syntax: CDSpeed speed

