@{fg shine}Function: CDTrackPlaying@{fg text}
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Modes : Amiga/Blitz
Syntax: num=CDTrackPlaying

  Returns the number of the currently playing cd track.

@ENDNODE CDTrackPlaying

